        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your litany rails against the sin of wrath, punishing the target for attacking good creatures. The target must attempt a Will save. A particularly wrathful creature, such as a wrath demon, uses the outcome one degree of success worse than the result of its saving throw. The target then becomes temporarily immune to all of your litanies for 1 minute.</p>\n<hr /><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The first time the target uses an action that deals damage to at least one good creature, the target takes 3d6 good damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> Each time the target uses an action that deals damage to at least one good creature, the target takes 3d6 good damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 2}. Each time it uses an action that deals damage to at least one good creature, the target takes 3d6 good damage.</p>\n<hr /><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The damage increases by 1d6."
